{"word":"ἡμερήσιος","slug":"ἡμερήσιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἡμερήσιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἡμέρα'><el>ἡμέρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>for the day, by day</i>, <el>ἡμ. φάος</el> light <i>as of the day</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a day long</i>, <el>ἡμ. ὁδός</el> a <i>day's</i> journey, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}